perfect for quiet reading and reflection.  A large loom lies at the foot of an
enormous tapestry which hangs on the south wall between the gap in the
bookshelves.  A tiny wind chime hangs in the east window, dwarfed even further
by the massive size of the window, sounding out in response to the wind.    
